like":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T23:58:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>村村住家窩面改左名未</blockquote><br />\n正正住家鍋麵  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好似未"},{"pid":"e88deb886aa30f6d18d8a6fe3faf44dd11c4cdc2","tid":156331,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T00:02:53.000Z","msg":"我認為呂以村先生既才能勁過肯德基伯伯<br />\n<br />\n肯德基伯伯淨係識整雞<br />\n<br />\n呂以村先生才華洋溢<br />\n<br />\n識整手攪面，村村住家窩面，過山雞，滷大腸，十三會<br />\n<br />\n求其一種都獨當一面<br />\n<br />\n相比肯德基淨係識整雞"},{"pid":"25d0d30bcf5b7264786a12883843fbc9a1913b84","tid":156331,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T00:03:52.000Z","msg":"而我認為除非譚仔同佢三哥聯手<br />\n<br />\n否則呂以村先生單打獨鬥下必輕取二人"},{"pid":"e47d6b5ae89b52373f98ee51f3d67744b52db677","tid":156331,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T00:04:48.000Z","msg":"呂以村先生贏過食神挑戰賽第二<br />\n<br />\n你可能話，<br />\n<br />\n點解贏唔到第一？<br />\n<br />\n因為呂先生既大絕手攪面當年仲未完成<br />\n<br />\n如今呂先生既手攪面已經獨霸美食界<br />\n<br />\n每條面都用捕獲等級4200既奇蹟小麥精製<br />\n<br />\n手攪面以呂先生既80G臂力攪成<br />\n<br />\n其QQ程度無法抗拒"},{"pid":"b4118896c22195c0a7113649e233ed1f101d5e13","tid":156331,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T00:05:06.000Z","msg":"屈機男出現了"},{"pid":"571ae384bd34c6172b2f8bea567f60543e3ce398","tid":156331,"uid":33787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T00:06:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"65bee85f7037ad1625f06e03d859a6059d08cc0a","tid":156331,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T00:06:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://profile.ak.fbcdn.net/hprofile-ak-snc4/41784_7533757190_9569_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fprofile.ak.fbcdn.net%2Fhprofile-ak-snc4%2F41784_7533757190_9569_n.jpg&h=59507a69&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我同呂以村先生傾過計<br />\n<br />\n我dup 低頭食緊十三會手攪面時<br />\n<br />\n見到隔離有人影企左起度<br />\n<br />\n一抬頭<br />\n<br />\n原來係呂以村先生<br />\n<br />\n佢望住我笑咪咪<br />\n<br />\n我唔知點好<br />\n<br />\n就同佢講<br />\n<br />\n你d面好好食呀！<br />\n<br />\n佢好客氣咁講<br />\n<br />\n多謝，多謝<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n佢一直企起度望住我食完為止 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"446134efb5b45be33ab9add7ca477152604e34cd","tid":156331,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T00:07:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呂以村好撚霸氣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n聽講每間舖都有套戰甲同金槍比佢隨時變身"},{"pid":"8dabde422f143ad6391d513177143d1b6d66e9f6","tid":156331,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T00:09:10.000Z","msg":"你入呂以村先生間舖<br />\n<br />\n門面，招牌<br />\n<br />\n的確係好柒<br />\n<br />\n但你會見到每一細節<br />\n<br />\n確係花過心機<br />\n<br />\n由餐牌，牆身呂以村先生既介紹<br />\n<br />\n你都睇到熱誠認真"},{"pid":"8fafcb7a7d214e3b4b9ff42fa652cd93bd0acf1c","tid":156331,"uid":90535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T00:14:10.000Z","msg":"金槍人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"759bce076655e2dfde026586e5527d24bf951c89","tid":156331,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T00:17:00.000Z","msg":"是日午餐一於食大家食J"},{"pid":"3622abb823ff1bc182c5c42e32dd543daaec30ae","tid":156331,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T00:22:13.000Z","msg":"食過一次，係幾好食"},{"pid":"bc69b32890e5155423df8d15b50d12b731562300","tid":156331,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T00:23:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食過一次，係幾好食</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 良心user"},{"pid":"dd9220e1914ad8a1f50a68c2c78b19fa7ff3ae27","tid":156331,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T00:24:42.000Z","msg":"之前高登飲食台大家食之亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi